associated with carbon materialsbetter source needed this breakthrough led to the development of new technologies and products including aqueous inkjet colorants for printer ink the basis of cabots inkjet colorants business unit which was founded in  in  cabot developed a commercialized process that allows continuous production of aerogels under ambient conditions which was the start of the company’s aerogel business in  cabot completed construction of and began operating two additional rubber black production plants at its carbon black plant in tianjin china increasing capacity to  metric tons in july  cabot purchased norit nv the largest producer of activated carbon for  billion cabot sold its supermetals business which produced tantalum niobium and related alloys in  to global advanced metals pty ltd safety health and environmentaledit safety recordedit the company has reduced total recordable injuries by over  in the last five years however the company experienced two fatalities in  the severity of incidents has caused the company to look at all aspects of workplace safetybetter source needed environmental recordedit sam bodman ceo of cabot during the coltan boom was appointed in december  to serve as president bush’s secretary of energy under bodman’s leadership from  to  according to jason leopold cabot was one of the us’s largest polluters accounting for  tons of airborne toxic emissions annually cabot reduced its environmental nonconformance events encs from a high of over  incidences in  to  in fy better source needed the company defines an environmental nonconformance event as a reportable spill or release a notice of violation a public complaint or certain permit deviations the company invested over  million in fy  on environmentallyrelated capital projects to improve efficiency and maintain regulatory compliance the company’s goal is a  reduction in greenhouse gas emission intensity by  using  as the baseline year one example of greenhouse gas reduction is a heat recovery advancement project to convert exhaust heat to steam at the company’s fumed metal oxides plant in rheinfelden germany the steam produced is used in the plant if needed or sold to a neighboring company the project has the potential to reduce ghg emissions by  mts each yearbetter source needed responsible careedit in  cabot joined the american chemistry council and as such is obliged to implement the council’s responsible care program as part of a global initiative cabot is implementing rc  which incorporates the requirements of both the acc responsible care and the iso  management systems for all its manufacturing facilities beginning with those in north america sustainabilityedit cabot’s  sustainability report titled sustainability matters cabot corporation’s  sustainability report met all the informational requirements to receive an application level c certification from the global reporting initiatives cabot’s adherence to gri reporting standards affirms its commitment to more transparent and thorough reporting awardsedit in  cabot corporation was selected as a bronze winner for the ninth annual team massachusetts economic impact awards they were also selected as one of cr magazine’s  best corporate citizens for  the american chemistry council honored cabot with the responsible care performance award in april  for helping the acc meet industrywide safety and product stewardship targets in april  cabot ranked fortyfourth among the top  leading companies that demonstrated superior management mitigation and adaptation in the field of climate innovation cabot was awarded a  leadership award for the massachusetts excellence in commuter options awards board of directorsedit cabot corporation’s board of directors is chaired by nonexecutive john f obrien retired president and chief executive officer allmerica financial corp cabot foundationedit in  the nonprofit cabot corporation foundation inc was established and the foundations charter was amended in  to permit grants to qualified charitable organizations outside of the united statesbetter source needed cabot has offered aid to earthquake victims in japan and the outward bound organization see alsoedit list of companies in the united states list of sp  companies referencesedit  cabot corp cbt new york bloomberg businessweek   a b cabot corporation  annual report cabot corporation  p    sustainability matters pdf cabot corporations sustainability  update cabot corporation   particle design for performance cabot corporation   surface modification ocp inks   aerogel history part ii nmc netlink   history of aerogels cabot corporation   resnickault jessica june   cabot corp to buy norit for  billion add activated carbon bloomberg   cabot supermetals unit now part of gam family metalbulletin   sustainability matters     sustainability update pdf cabot corporation   safety performance cabot corporation   the environment is doomed the huffington post  retrieved    cabot  annual report pdf cabot corporation   sustainability matters   sustainability update pdf cabot corporation   cabot corporation issues  sustainability report wwwprnewswirecom  retrieved    responsible care international council of chemical associations   cabot corporation to implement responsible care in north america businesswire retrieved february     cabot issues  sustainability report update marketwatch retrieved august     cabot corporation selected as a bronze winner for the ninth annual team massachusetts economic impact awards msn money retrieved october     crs  best corporate citizens  pdf cr magazine retrieved   check date values in accessdate help  heumann jenny chemical industry honors companies for excellent performance and commitment to health and safety american chemistry council retrieved april     cabot ranks th in maplecroft climate innovation index businesswire retrieved april     climate innovation indexes maplecroft   massachusetts excellence in commuter options eco awards massrides