l’s prestigious learn more collaboration  innovation switch to d and see the positive difference d learn more best in class cmp polishing pads learn more total quality take the journey discover cabot microelectronics cabot microelectronics corporation headquartered in aurora illinois is the worlds leading supplier of chemical mechanical planarization cmp polishing slurries used in semiconductor manufacturing and second largest cmp pads supplier to the semiconductor industry our products play a critical role in the production of advanced semiconductor devices helping to enable the manufacture of smaller faster and more complex devices by our customers our mission is to create value by delivering highperforming and innovative solutions that solve our customers’ challenges cmp slurries as a pioneer in chemical mechanical planarization cmp slurries cabot microelectronics commercialized our original semisperse™ products in the s for nm applications learn more   cmp polishing pads cabot microelectronics’ epic™ and nexplanar® pads enable us to deliver a broad range of cmp polishing pad solutions including performancedifferentiated slurry and pad consumable sets learn more   cmp best practices as a proud partner to the semiconductor industry cabot microelectronics is pleased to provide you with educational tools to help you optimize chemical mechanical planarization cmp process reliability and performance learn more   about usoverview mission vision and values executive officers global locations our offerings careers for investorssec filings press releases annual reports events  presentations quarterly results investor toolkit connect with cabot microelectronics contact us supplier portal technical resourcesbest practices copyright   cabot microelectronics  site map  site terms and conditions  privacy policy  california supply chains act back to top this website uses cookies by continuing to use this website you are consenting to the use of cookies for more information plea